-- Merafe Resources Advances After Saying It Returned to Profit in First Half
-- Carli Lourens
-- 2010-07-15T07:06:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/merafe-resources-advances-after-saying-it-returned-to-profit-in-first-half.html

          
          
             Merafe Resources Ltd. gained in
Johannesburg trading after saying its first-half profit was
between 7 cents and 8 cents a share.  
 Shares in the company rose as much as 3.1 percent to 1.34
rand and traded at 1.33 rand as of 9:03 a.m.  
          
          


  


        